word !important;"><br></section><section style="margin-top: -18px;padding: 6px;max-width: 100%;width: 25px;height: 25px;border-top-left-radius: 50%;border-top-right-radius: 50%;border-bottom-right-radius: 50%;border-bottom-left-radius: 50%;color: rgb(152, 0, 180);opacity: 0.6;background-color: rgb(255, 140, 0);line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></section></section><section style="max-width: 100%;width: 0px;height: 0px;clear: both;line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></section></section><section style="line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">有些人说小鸡不能喂水，喝了水会拉肚子死掉，其实这是不对的。</span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);">小鸡带回家后应尽快喂水</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">，喂水不及时才容易使小鸡因口渴狂饮而导致腹泻死亡。此外，先饮水再开食可以促进小鸡肠道蠕动，帮助吸收残余的蛋黄营养并排出胎粪。<br></span></section><section style="margin: 5px 8px;max-width: 100%;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></section></section><section style="line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">小鸡抵抗力差，所以喂水的时候要使用</span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);">蒸馏水</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">，而不能直接喂自来水，另外</span><span style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);"><strong>水的温度最好在30℃左右</strong></span><span style="font-size: 16px;">——手摸瓶子略觉温暖即可。小鸡初次饮水时不要喂太多，要始终遵循少量多次的原则，防止水太多喝不完而变质，或水不够导致小鸡脱水。</span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><br></section><section style="line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">小鸡的饮用水应在其中</span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);">加入5%葡萄糖</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">（如没有可用白糖代替）、</span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);">0.1%维生素C和0.6%食盐</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">，以增强体质。为了防止鸡白痢等疾病，可在水中再加入极少量的痢特灵（或氧氟沙星、土霉素、庆大霉素之一）。找一个洗净的可乐瓶来配小鸡饮料，瓶盖装平满是约10g食盐，以此来参考配制。特别提醒的是，</span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);">营养丰富的水容易引来细菌垂涎，记得要每天配新的喔</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">。在第一周都用这样的水喂小鸡，一周后就可以喂纯水或加入少量复合维生素B的水了。</span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br></span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.70625" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://1-im.guokr.com/WJMHUjoje7nxJ_1p7uEZpy4JPkfDeYlJ5chg9_2a7fCAAgAAxAEAAEpQ.jpg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="960" src="https://1-im.guokr.com/WJMHUjoje7nxJ_1p7uEZpy4JPkfDeYlJ5chg9_2a7fCAAgAAxAEAAEpQ.jpg?imageView2/1/w/555/h/391"><br><span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;">你以为养个鸡这么容易吗｜<span dir="ltr" style="unicode-bidi: isolate;margin-right: -2px;padding-right: 2px;overflow: hidden;text-overflow: ellipsis;">pixabay.com</span></span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178);unicode-bidi: isolate;margin-right: -2px;padding-right: 2px;overflow: hidden;text-overflow: ellipsis;font-size: 16px;"><br></span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">初次饮水后3小时左右，就可以给小鸡第一次喂食了，是不是很期待呢？和人类的宝宝一样，小鸡的消化道很脆弱，所以不能喂硬的东西，更要注意食物是否新鲜和干净。小鸡可以吃</span><span style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);"><strong>米饭、煮软的小米、调入温水的玉米面</strong></span><span style="font-size: 16px;">等食物。</span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><br></section><section style="line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">和饮水一样，小鸡应该使用</span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);">少吃多餐</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">的方式，因为它生长代谢快，但是肠胃容积小。前几天最好每2-3小时喂一次，以后可以渐渐减少到每天喂食4-6次，大约1周后就可以开始逐步喂食谷粒、玉米渣、洗净切碎的蔬菜等食物了。另外从喂硬食开始，也就应该找些沙砾来喂给小鸡，帮助它消化了。</span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><br></section><section style="line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">注意哟，</span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);">要想和小鸡培养感情，你可以在喂食前先喊小鸡的名字</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">，让它跑过来，再抛洒食物给它，这样几天之后小鸡就会和你变得很亲近，喜欢跟着你，十分可爱呢。记住，千万要耐心等小鸡来亲近你，不要随便用手去抓它，以免小鸡受到惊吓。</span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br></span></section><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.5em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.6635294117647059" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://3-im.guokr.com/gUS_gDfhaRmyqfDZ9EkTYK0RFZRdi3yMe9T9ONwK4PKpAQAAGgEAAEpQ.jpg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="425" src="https://3-im.guokr.com/gUS_gDfhaRmyqfDZ9EkTYK0RFZRdi3yMe9T9ONwK4PKpAQAAGgEAAEpQ.jpg"><br><span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178);line-height: 1.6;font-size: 12px;">吃东西什么的，最开心了｜twitter.com</span><span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178);line-height: 1.6;font-size: 16px;"></span></p><section style="line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><br></section><section style="max-width: 100%;font-family: 微软雅黑;line-height: 25.6px;white-space: normal;border: 0px none;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="max-width: 100%;border: 0px none;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin-right: auto;margin-left: auto;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin-top: 20px;max-width: 100%;border: 0px none;line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin-left: 40px;max-width: 100%;display: inline-block;color: inherit;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin-top: 0.2em;padding-right: 0.5em;padding-bottom: 5px;padding-left: 1.2em;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(121, 121, 121);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-style: solid;border-color: rgb(255, 140, 0);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(255, 104, 39);">我也可以很干净</span></strong></span></section><section style="margin: 5px 1.2em;max-width: 100%;line-height: 1;color: rgb(121, 121, 121);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section></section><section style="margin-top: -48px;padding: 9px;max-width: 100%;width: 40px;height: 40px;border-top-left-radius: 50%;border-top-right-radius: 50%;border-bottom-right-radius: 50%;border-bottom-left-radius: 50%;color: rgb(5, 115, 175);opacity: 0.6;background-color: rgb(255, 140, 0);line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></section><section style="margin-top: -18px;padding: 6px;max-width: 100%;width: 25px;height: 25px;border-top-left-radius: 50%;border-top-right-radius: 50%;border-bottom-right-radius: 50%;border-bottom-left-radius: 50%;color: rgb(152, 0, 180);opacity: 0.6;background-color: rgb(255, 140, 0);line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></section></section><section style="max-width: 100%;width: 0px;height: 0px;clear: both;line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></section></section><section style="line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">小朋友们总是喜欢带宠物出去玩，但是</span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);">雏鸡在3周内最好不要带出门</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">，一则它们还不能适应室外较低的温度，二则小鸡抵抗力还很弱，容易在外面染上疾病。当小鸡长到一个月大了，带出去时也要小心看护喔，小鸡可是好奇心非常旺盛的，看到什么都想啄一下，就算没有啄到小朋友，啄到花花草草也不好啊。<br></span></section><section style="margin: 5px 8px;max-width: 100%;line-height: 2em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></section></section><section style="line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);"><strong>小鸡有可能因为肛门堵塞无法正常排泄而死，</strong></span><span style="font-size: 16px;">所以在1周内都要早晚观察小鸡的肛门周围，如果出现脏污糊在毛上，就要及时用温水润湿，然后用棉球蘸水轻轻把污物擦去。谁让小鸡拉完便便不会自己擦屁屁呢……如果有条件，带小鸡去养鸡场等专业的地方进行疫苗滴鼻或注射免疫最好啦。</span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br></span></section><p style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.5em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="1" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://3-im.guokr.com/3Vb5BzLRJ16TlJKWIMnI1T1sMyHnWDm07XAFpEVLsJWAAgAAgAIAAEpQ.jpg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" src="https://3-im.guokr.com/3Vb5BzLRJ16TlJKWIMnI1T1sMyHnWDm07XAFpEVLsJWAAgAAgAIAAEpQ.jpg?imageView2/1/w/555/h/555"><br><span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;">“咦，你也是金黄色的哎” ｜daliulian.net</span></p><section style="line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 16px;"><br></span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">由于可能涉及的传染病，如禽流感等，一般是通过空气传播或接触到污染的粪便等而传播，所以</span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);">鸡窝里铺的报纸要每天多次更换，喂食的碟子也应该每天清洗，同时家里要注意保持良好的通风，小朋友跟小鸡玩耍后要及时洗手</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">，这样就可以避免疾病的传播，同时家里也不会有臭味了。</span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><br></section><section style="line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">虽然要注意干净，可是</span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);">千万不要给小鸡洗澡喔</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">！鸡是用“干洗”的方式来保持自身清洁的，等小鸡长大后，带它出门玩，它就会在沙子里洗澡的。</span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><br></section><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-ratio="0.66640625" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://3-im.guokr.com/_ut-m7inSdV8aYcSQd1PsVaOgvvwKDAXXb3I1HXhQzY4BAAA0AIAAEpQ.jpg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1280" style="" src="https://3-im.guokr.com/_ut-m7inSdV8aYcSQd1PsVaOgvvwKDAXXb3I1HXhQzY4BAAA0AIAAEpQ.jpg?imageView2/1/w/555/h/370"></p><section style="margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.5em;"><span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;">不要给我洗澡哦｜Pixabay</span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br></span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">对了，春季是各大养鸡场育雏的旺季，为了节省育雏房舍、设备和饲料，蛋鸡的雏鸡出壳后会面临雌雄筛选，将公鸡及早淘汰，这就是市售小鸡的来源。所以，如果小贩挑给你两只小鸡、说那是一公一母，这种话千万别信。</span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><br></span></section><section powered-by="xiumi.us" style='margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;word-wrap: break-word !important;'><section style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;display: flex;align-items: center;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;flex: 1 1 auto;height: 1px;background-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><svg viewbox="0 0 1 1" style="float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;"></svg></section></section><section style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;flex: 0 1 auto;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section opera-tn-ra-cell="_$.pages:0.layers:0.comps:43.col1" style="padding-right: 15px;padding-left: 15px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section powered-by="xiumi.us" style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: center;color: rgb(205, 204, 204);font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.61;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178);">参考文献</span><br style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p></section></section></section><section style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;flex: 1 1 auto;height: 1px;transform: matrix(-1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0);background-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><svg viewbox="0 0 1 1" style="float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;"></svg></section></section></section></section><section powered-by="xiumi.us" style='padding-right: 8px;padding-left: 8px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.61;color: rgb(205, 204, 204);font-size: 12px;word-wrap: break-word 